{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-v9/lab-optional-arguments-sum-function/build-an-optional-arguments-sum-function","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"lab-optional-arguments-sum-function","demoType":null,"title":"Izgradnja generalne funkcionalnosti za opcione argumente","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U ovom okruženju ćete napraviti funkciju koja prihvata do dva argumenta i sabira ih, ali ako postoji samo jedan argument, funkcija će vratiti drugu funkciju koja čeka drugi broj za sabiranje.</p>\n<p><strong>Cilj:</strong> Popunite korisničke priče navedene ispod i prođite sve testove kako biste završili laboratorijum.</p>\n<p>Priče o korisniku:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Kreiraj funkciju <code>addTogether</code>.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Ako funkcija prima dva argumenta, funkcija treba da vrati zbir ova dva argumenta.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Ako je dostavljen samo jedan argument, <code>addTogether</code> treba da vrati funkciju.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Funkcija koja je vraćena kada se pozove sa jednim argumentom, treba da vrati zbir.</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">const sumTwoAnd = addTogether(2);\r\nsumTwoAnd(3); // 5\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Ako bilo koji argument nije važeći broj, vrati <code>undefined</code>.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</section>","id":"a97fd23d9b809dac9921074f","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":26,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-v9","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-v9/lab-optional-arguments-sum-function/build-an-optional-arguments-sum-function"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da imaš funkciju <code>addTogether</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isFunction(addTogether);"},{"text":"<p><code>addTogether(2, 3)</code> trebalo bi da vrati 5.</p>","testString":"assert.deepEqual(addTogether(2, 3), 5);"},{"text":"<p><code>addTogether(23.4, 30)</code> treba da vrati 53.4.</p>","testString":"assert.deepEqual(addTogether(23.4, 30), 53.4);"},{"text":"<p><code>addTogether(\"2\", 3)</code> trebalo bi vratiti <code>undefined</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isUndefined(addTogether('2', 3));"},{"text":"<p><code>addTogether(5, undefined)</code> treba da vrati <code>undefined</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isUndefined(addTogether(5, undefined));"},{"text":"<p><code>addTogether(\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ\")</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>undefined</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isUndefined(addTogether('https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ'));"},{"text":"<p><code>addTogether(5)</code> Trebalo bi da vrati funkciju.</p>","testString":"assert.isFunction(addTogether(5));"},{"text":"<p><code>addTogether(5)(7)</code> Trebalo bi da vrati 12.</p>","testString":"assert.deepEqual(addTogether(5)(7), 12);"},{"text":"<p><code>addTogether(2)([3])</code> trebalo bi vratiti <code>undefined</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isUndefined(addTogether(2)([3]));"},{"text":"<p><code>addTogether(2, \"3\")</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>undefined</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isUndefined(addTogether(2, '3'));"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-v9/#lab-optional-arguments-sum-function","dashedName":"build-an-optional-arguments-sum-function","certification":"javascript-v9","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-v9","chapter":"javascript","module":"functional-programming","block":"lab-optional-arguments-sum-function","isFirstStep":true,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":true,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-v9/lab-sorting-visualizer/build-a-sorting-visualizer","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-v9/workshop-recipe-ingredient-converter/step-18","id":"a97fd23d9b809dac9921074f","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":26,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function addTogether() {\r\n  const first = arguments[0];\r\n  if (typeof(first) !== 'number') {\r\n    return undefined;\r\n  }\r\n  if (arguments.length === 1) {\r\n    return function(second) {\r\n      if (typeof(second) !== 'number') {\r\n        return undefined;\r\n      }\r\n      return first + second;\r\n    };\r\n  }\r\n  const second = arguments[1];\r\n  if (typeof(second) !== 'number') {\r\n    return undefined;\r\n  }\r\n  return first + second;\r\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javascript-v9/lab-optional-arguments-sum-function/build-an-optional-arguments-sum-function"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}